Introduction
Structured prompting techniques improve AI responses by providing clear instructions, defining roles, controlling formatting, changing writing styles, and separating inputs using delimiters. These techniques produce accurate, organized, and practical outputs.
1. Instruction Tuning
Exercise 1 – Customer Reminder Email
Subject: Software License Renewal Reminder

